title: American Greetings All-Occasion Gift Tags, Multicolor Assortment (100-Count)
description: You bought the gift, now don’t forget to tag yourself! This set of 100 multi-color gift tags from American Greetings is perfect to use for celebrations all year round! The 2 x 3-inch tags are blank so you can add a personal message to your loved ones! The set comes in a rainbow of colors, with 100 feet of white ribbon for attaching. Great for birthdays, Christmas, and all sorts of occasions, finish off your thoughtful gift with colorful gift tags from American Greetings!
